# PR #55 审查报告

> 审查范围：`feat/issue-43`（Matching 模块：推荐卡片、滑动匹配、双向配对、匹配列
表）
> 审查依据：`AGENTS.md`、`docs/design-docs/api.md`、`docs/design-docs/nestjs.md`
、`docs/design-docs/flutter.md`、`docs/design-docs/db.md`、`prd/v1-matching.md`
、`docs/exec-plans/TASK-matching.md`、`docs/modules/matching.md`

